<% content_for :title, "About The FUPRE Info Portal" %>

<h1 class="mb-4">About The FUPRE Info Portal</h1>

<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-8 mb-4">
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body p-4">
        <h2 class="card-title h1 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
        <p class="fs-5">In a bustling university environment, staying informed is key. The FUPRE Info Portal was born out of a need to bridge the communication gap between the university administration and our vibrant student community. We believe that timely and accessible information is the bedrock of a thriving academic ecosystem.</p>
        <p class="fs-5">Our mission is to provide a centralized, user-friendly platform for all official announcements, memos, and events. We're here to ensure you never miss a beat, from critical academic deadlines to exciting campus happenings.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
    <div class="card shadow-sm">
      <div class="card-body p-4">
        <h2 class="card-title h1 mb-4">What You'll Find</h2>
        <ul class="list-unstyled fs-5">
          <li class="mb-3"><i class="fas fa-home me-2"></i><strong>Dashboard:</strong> Your one-stop overview of the latest updates.</li>
          <li class="mb-3"><i class="fas fa-bullhorn me-2"></i><strong>Announcements:</strong> All official circulars and memos, right at your fingertips.</li>
          <li class="mb-3"><i class="fas fa-calendar-alt me-2"></i><strong>Events:</strong> Stay on top of the academic calendar and campus events.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
